f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n管理處話下晝會交代詳情，狗點入大堂之類"},{"pid":"0d97b86024a9ba4d3f385263f83b9d810ef2df14","tid":1700971,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瞄頭射殺，連開三鎗</span>"},{"pid":"80460936398d5c3da38edf6c64b5880e34d471c2","tid":1700971,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa498e024bd2767b5e17e81a46275a8644725e95","tid":1700971,"uid":271123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:28:10.000Z","msg":"早兩年仲有個女警係地鐵站射死個拎𠝹刀阿叔，之後比人影到佢射死人仲係到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"好似冇咁耐之前"},{"pid":"3a6988b22c796cbd16fa2e9c183222d87860f531","tid":1700971,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"4be31c88620672ddadb1466d35049ea48305da5a","tid":1700971,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:14:48.000Z","msg":"仆街黑警"},{"pid":"4f4fd9dadefe7e3c74304a7935f9f2a2d53beec2","tid":1700971,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"Push 3"}]}